test_even_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6] == [4, 6, 8, 10, 12]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 4
  Left contains one more item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [4, 6, 8, 10, 12]
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
test_large_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6] == [2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 2
  Left contains one more item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
  ?  +++
